<p>Source: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://psephos.adam-carr.net/countries/u/usa/pres.shtml">Presidential Elections 1789–2000</a> at <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://psephos.adam-carr.net/">Psephos (Adam Carr's Election Archive)</a><br />
