<li id="cite_note-auto1-31"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="Electoral_College_(United_States)#cite_ref-auto1_31-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="Electoral_College_(United_States)#cite_ref-auto1_31-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Hamilton, Alexander. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.constitution.org/fed/federa68.htm">Federalist No. 68</a>, The Constitution Society, viewed online March 2, 2019.</span>
