<li id="cite_note-Madison_to_Hay,_1823-38"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="Electoral_College_(United_States)#cite_ref-Madison_to_Hay,_1823_38-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="Electoral_College_(United_States)#cite_ref-Madison_to_Hay,_1823_38-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20170525182347/https://founders.archives.gov/documents/Madison/99-02-02-0023">"Founders Online: James Madison to George Hay, 23 August 1823"</a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://founders.archives.gov/documents/Madison/99-02-02-0023">the original</a> on May 25, 2017.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Founders+Online%3A+James+Madison+to+George+Hay%2C+23+August+1823&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Ffounders.archives.gov%2Fdocuments%2FMadison%2F99-02-02-0023&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AUnited+States+Electoral+College" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
