<li id="cite_note-50"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Electoral_College_(United_States)#cite_ref-50">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Brian D. Humes, Elaine K. Swift, Richard M. Valley, Kenneth Finegold, and Evelyn C. Fink, "Repres